able Basecamp Gas Stove</h3><p style=\"margin:4px 0;color:#555;\">Fire Maple</p><p style=\"margin:4px 0;\"><strong>$108.00</strong> at time of publishing</p><p style=\"margin:8px 0 0 0;\"><a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=37934&#038;awinaffid=1923681&#038;ued=https%3A%2F%2Ffiremaplegear.com%2Fproducts%2Ffms-108-gas-stove%3Fvariant%3D39742212997216\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer sponsored\" style=\"background:#8920F3;color:#fff;padding:10px 18px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;display:inline-block;\">Check Price &rarr;</a></p></div></div><div class=\"pros-cons-grid\" style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-top:16px;\"><div style=\"background:#f0fbf4;border-radius:8px;padding:14px;\"><strong style=\"color:#1a7a3d;\">Pros</strong><ul style=\"margin:8px 0 0 0;padding-left:18px;\"><li>A Taller Basecamp Cooking Setup.Built for car camping, basecamps, and shared outdoor meals, the FMS-108 combines adjustable legs, wide cookware support, and 3.5 kW output. A preheat tube and inverted-canister bracket add a liquid-feed option for colder conditions after proper warm-up.</li><li>Sold under the established Fire Maple brand</li></ul></div><div style=\"background:#fdf3f3;border-radius:8px;padding:14px;\"><strong style=\"color:#a33;\">Cons</strong><ul style=\"margin:8px 0 0 0;padding-left:18px;\"><li>No standout drawback versus the other options compared here</li></ul></div></div><div style=\"margin-top:14px;font-size:15px;\"><p style=\"margin:6px 0;\"><strong>Best suited for:</strong> Buyers who want a balance of price and features without going to either extreme.</p><p style=\"margin:6px 0;\"><strong>Consider the alternative if:</strong> If you specifically need premium extras, the higher-priced pick in this set may suit better.</p><p style=\"margin:6px 0;\"><strong>Value for money:</strong> Mid-to-upper pricing relative to the other options compared here.</p></div></div><div style=\"border